. Furthermore, the topmost detection accuracy and\ncompetitive speed are achieved by our method compared with other\ndomain-specific,e.g., DAPN, PADN, and general CNN-based methods,e.g., FPN,\nCascade R-CNN, SSD, RefineDet and RPDet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 16:54:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 04:37:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-20"}
