ced in significance. Based on these results, we\nfurther constrain the neutrino flux spatially correlated with UHECRs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 21:07:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 18:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2022 12:26:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
