\nexplain both anomalies simultaneously. Next we study the scalar contribution\nand show that the scalar contributions can explain both anomalies\nsimultaneously. My third work investigate the diverse FCNCs within the same\nsecond BSM model to constrain mass range of vector-like fermions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 15:31:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-20"}
