ally\nquasi-Toeplitz Markov chains (AQTMC). For the approximate computation of the\nstationary distribution, a new approach is developed.\n  An optimization problem to obtain optimal value of total number of backup\nchannels has been formulated and dealt by employing non dominated sorting\ngenetic algorithm-II (NSGA-II) approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 12:52:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-21"}
